      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CALLA NAUGHTY (2) has missed the frame at her last two but did run well three back when third (17.87) in a NG at this track. Key player on best and worth another chance. MAJESTIC EMMY (5) failed to come into contention last start after drifting back at Capalaba, but prior to that won by 2.25 lengths at this track (17.28) beating Fire And Gravy in a Grade 5 on January 14. Should be in this for a long way. RUBY ON SCOTCH (7) finds it hard to break through. Finished in the money last time though when third (17.72) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Expected to be in this for a long way. TIDE IN (1) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
